metadata.name: Takamuto #1626
metadata.description: TAKAMUTO is a collection of 5,000 hand drawn NFTs living on the Ethereum blockchain, created from a combination of 36 traits with varying rarity across different categories. There will be some special 1/1s sprinkled in the collection, and you might get lucky and mint one with a trait from your favorite project! Our vision is to bring more joy to the world and bring people together through community, creativity, and fun art!
